bool landmark::Landmark::learnMinMax ( const cv::Mat  image,
const cv::Point  offset,
Descriptor &  descriptor,
std::vector< cv::Point >  blob_contours 
)

Learn landmark detection from image.

learn landmark: Learn a singular landmark descriptor from an image. In the very first image, the desired landmark must be the largest blob in the scene. Returns true when succeed, otherwise false.

Parameters
imagean image to extract blobs from
offsetan offset in respect to original image. If not using ROI, set to (0,0).
descriptorcurrent landmark descriptor (returning value).
blob_contourscontours of the detected landmark (returning value).
